      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for an experienced mechanic or someone looking for a major project. While the car is currently tow-away only due to significant transmission slipping and a heavy oil leak, the frame remains relatively solid. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functioning climate control system, and the exterior has several noticeable dents and peeling clear coat. It is being sold strictly as-is, with no guarantees, but could serve as a valuable source of parts or a complete restoration candidate for the right buyer.",
