      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has clearly been well-cared for over the years\u2014super clean inside and out! It runs like a dream and is totally ready to hit the road with its next owner. If you're looking for something reliable and stylish that's ready for its next adventure, you've found it! Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
