    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies. This example retains its mechanical integrity with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a functional variable M differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring chassis rigidity under lateral load. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative steering feedback these chassis are known for. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its status, the engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline with no hesitation. A visceral, naturally aspirated experience for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
